# Uppercase or Lowercase Checker
This program asks the user to type a word and then checks whether the first character is uppercase or lowercase.

# Features
- Asks the user to input a word
- Checks if the first character is uppercase
- Checks if the first character is lowercase
- Displays the results as True or False

# How to use
Run the program and type any word when prompted.
The program will show whether the first letter is uppercase or lowercase.




# Learning Purpose
This project was created as part of my backend engineering practice.
The goal was to improve my skills in Python, string indexing, user input handling, and character checking methods.
